name: Many Ways To Death
description:
Death is a certainty, and loneliness always accompanies it. Loneliness is like a heart that has been stolen and stabbed many times.




Kematian adalah kepastian, dan kesendirian selalu menemaninya. Kesepian itu laksana hati yang dicuri dan ditikam berkali-kali.
